title: '"Some sectors ... have special provisions for the determination of their taxable income, such as the financial sector, the oil, gas and mining sector, the international transport sector, gas stations, leasing companies, insurance companies, bookshops and construction services. Concessions also receive a special tax treatment."'
pid: 8f0819cb-3f32-4a77-bef3-c75f20bbd24b
body: |2-
  Punishes capital-intensive endeavors.
